profile: Residential foundation repair and waterproofing service. Contract work. We repair cracked and/or leaking foundations in the Greater Sudbury, ON area. We handle the excavation and removal of dirt around your home, provide any needed structural repair, waterproofing with foundation emulsion and dimpled membrane, installation of weeping tile with filter cloth, sump-pit installation, insulation for added protection, and back-fill. Complete foundation waterproofing service helping basements keep dry for years to come. Visit our website to see if we are right for you.
